metadata.name: Forgotten Fantasy
metadata.description:
Follow the rainbow through the fairy tale pages of this forgotten fantasy. Inspired by video game and storybook fantasy worlds.

If this series generates any interest I will be posting more from this AI series.

This is the first NFT I have ever made. I was on the fence about releasing artwork on this platform but I figured why not give it a try. 

Whoever buys this NFT can request the original loop of any resolution up to 4K.
